ed on, for example:\r\n\r\nIt most recently worked on: Rust 1.47\r\n-->\r\n\r\nIt most recently worked on: 1.56.0-beta.4\r\n\r\n### Version with regression\r\n\r\n<!--\r\nProvide the version you are using that has the regression.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n`rustc --version --verbose`:\r\n```\r\nrustc 1.57.0-nightly (485ced56b 2021-10-07)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: 485ced56b8753ec86936903f2a8c95e9be8996a1\r\ncommit-date: 2021-10-07\r\nhost: x86_64-pc-windows-msvc\r\nrelease: 1.57.0-nightly\r\nLLVM version: 13.0.0\r\n```\r\n\r\n@rustbot modify labels: +regression-from-stable-to-nightly -regression-untriaged +O-windows\r\n\r\ncc @seanyoung ", "closed_by": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89658/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89658/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}